# Runtime log (rotating file handler in app_log.py)
fctool.log
fctool.log.*

# stargate_jumps.json is intentionally committed: it is bundled by FCTool.spec
# (a static EVE SDE stargate graph), so the source must build from a clean clone.

# system_coords.json is intentionally committed: it is bundled by FCTool.spec
# (a static New Eden coordinate table generated by tools/gen_system_coords.py),
# so the source must build from a clean clone.

# fit_types.json is intentionally committed: it is bundled by FCTool.spec
# (a static typeID->name/category/slot table generated by tools/gen_fit_types.py),
# so the source must build from a clean clone. The runtime ESI-fallback cache
# (fit_types_cache.json) and the user library (fittings_library.json) are ignored above.

